# MailChimp MCP Server Configuration
#
# Create ~/.mailchimp-mcp/config.json with these values:
#
# {
#   "api_key": "your-api-key-us21",
#   "server_prefix": "us21"
# }
#
# Notes:
# - api_key: Generate at Account > Extras > API Keys
# - server_prefix: The datacenter suffix from your API key (e.g. "us21" from "abc123-us21")
